The purpose of this study is to determine how safe and effective allantoin 3% cream (Alwextin) is in improving the healing of recurrent skin lesions and reducing overall blistering in people with epidermolysis bullosa (EB).

 Allantoin 3% cream is applied topically to the entire body once daily.

